---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Story — AcaiFlow" description="Eat well, feel good. The story behind AcaiFlow.">
  <PageHero
    image="/heroes/story.jpg"
    eyebrow="our story"
    title="eat well, feel good"
  />

  <section class="bg-cream-warm">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32 text-coffee text-lg leading-[1.8]">
      <p class="italic-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-ink leading-snug mb-12">
        Eating healthy isn't always easy, but we believe it should be.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-7">That's why we started AcaiFlow.</p>

      <p class="mb-7">
        We're here to make wholesome eating easy, so you can focus on feeling your best every day. No strict diets, confusing choices, or boring salads. Just balanced bowls made with wholesome ingredients that support your energy and wellbeing.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-7">
        We believe in honest food made for real life — meals that nourish your body and fit naturally into your routine.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-7">
        And here's how we bring it all together: wholesome grains, fresh vegetables, quality proteins, healthy fats, and house-made dressings. All of this comes together in a seasonal menu that keeps every bowl vibrant, balanced, and made to help you eat well and feel good.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-12">
        There's never a dull bowl at AcaiFlow, and we're pretty sure any choice you make will be a good one.
      </p>

      <p class="italic-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-ink leading-snug">
        Let's build your bowl.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a
          href="/menu"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-ink text-cream-warm text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] px-7 py-3 hover:bg-berry transition-colors"
        >
          See the menu
        </a>
        <a
          href="/calculator"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-ink text-ink text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] px-7 py-3 hover:bg-ink hover:text-cream-warm transition-colors"
        >
          Build a bowl
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
